Feline2::'
She was in the CR when she woke up. She was still feeling groggy, but 
her chest was healed. She stepped out of the CR and looked around.
She saw HotRod there near the CR. "Why did you do that? Your a 
maximal now. I'm a predacon. Why do you do these things. I don't 
understand." She was looking at him, with fear growing in her spark. 
She couldn't understand why she felt this way. She was feeling 
someting inside her spark and it was growing. She cared for him. But 
she wasn't sure why. She was scared because her instincts told her to 
never trust a maximal. But here she was, falling in love with one.  
All she cold do was stare at him. She couldn't even move. Her spark 
was racing in her chest, from fear or love, she wasn
t sure which it was.
